" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 524px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    FDG-PET/CT of a malignant lung mass",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 389px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The image demonstrates a malignant lung mass as seen on an integrated 18-fluoro-2-deoxyglucose positron emission tomography and computed tomography (FDG-PET/CT) scan. The increased activity of the mass is the result of the uptake and accumulation of FDG by the metabolically active tumor cells.",
