"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?0/35/568?source=see_link\">",
"      Clinical presentation and patterns of disease distribution in classical Hodgkin lymphoma in adults",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?10/29/10711?source=see_link\">",
