"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?37/7/38009?source=see_link\">",
"      Second and third line chemotherapy regimens and biologic therapy for relapsing or resistant classical Hodgkin lymphoma",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?34/26/35242?source=see_link\">",
